##
## Upstream tests to disable
##
## When adding a new filter to this list, please include a short description of
## why the filter is required and create an associated tracking issue.
##

# Known upstream flake (crbug.com/40831552): ~1% flake rate over 30 days per
# LUCI Analysis. Already disabled on Android upstream. DCHECK failure in
# MockResultQueue::NextOperationResult due to MOCK_TIME auto-advancing the
# PurgeStale timer during TestFuture::Take(), consuming an extra mock queue
# entry. Same root cause affects both FileBacked and InMemoryOnly variants.
-All/SharedStorageManagerErrorParamTest.InitFailure_DestroyAndRecreateDatabase/FileBacked
-All/SharedStorageManagerErrorParamTest.OtherOperationResults_NoErrorsAdded/FileBacked
-All/SharedStorageManagerErrorParamTest.OtherOperationResults_NoErrorsAdded/InMemoryOnly

# These tests fail because we override Prefetch methods to do nothing.
-AffiliationServiceImplTest.*

